# Upload To Mikesendpoint

## TRIGGER
When the user says "upload to mikesendpoint" or similar phrases, deploy the current workspace to a subdomain at mikesendpoint.com.

## PURPOSE
Universal deployment command that works from ANY repo. Automatically uses the workspace folder name as the subdomain.

## FULL IMPLEMENTATION
When trigger detected, read complete implementation:
```powershell
$content = Get-Content "C:/Users/mike.ullman/OneDrive - Vizio, Inc/Documents/Cline/Rules/full/upload-to-mikesendpoint.md" -Raw
```

Or use read_file tool:
`full/upload-to-mikesendpoint.md`